lights at a simple intersection.  Take the implementation we did in
class (<a href="trafficlights.circ"><b>trafficlights.circ</b></a>) and
reimplement it in ROM using the microcode approach.  Make your circuit
as simple as possible.  (although using the 3-alow-sr subcircuit is
100% ok)
